    <item>
      <title>财政司司长表示香港不会征收离境税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/hong-kong-won-t-impose-departure-tax-says-finance-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港财政司司长陈茂波表示，他没有计划向居民征收离境税，并拒绝了旨在缓解政府不断扩大的赤字的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/hong-kong-won-t-impose-departure-tax-says-finance-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:52:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着通胀加速，交易员认为英国央行降息幅度较小</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/traders-aggressively-pare-boe-rate-cut-bets-after-cpi-quickens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示通胀10个月来首次意外上升后，交易员大幅削减了对英国央行降息的押注，英国债券大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/traders-aggressively-pare-boe-rate-cut-bets-after-cpi-quickens</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:12:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>太阳能电池板制造商因考虑关闭德国工厂而股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/swiss-solar-panel-maker-weighs-closing-german-unit-amid-us-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士太阳能电池板制造商梅耶博格科技股份公司 (Meyer Burger Technology AG) 表示可能关闭欧洲最大的生产基地之一并将重心转向美国，股价暴跌 47%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/swiss-solar-panel-maker-weighs-closing-german-unit-amid-us-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 07:20:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
